---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
---

<Layout title="Guide de l'Athlète - Elsassman Triathlon" lang="fr">
    <Navbar lang="fr" />
    
    <main class="pt-32 pb-20 container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black uppercase mb-4 text-white">Guide de <span class="text-brand-secondary">l'Athlète</span></h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Informations essentielles pour préparer votre course. N'oubliez rien le jour J !</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Swim -->
            <div class="glass-panel p-8 rounded-xl hover:border-brand-primary/50 transition-colors group">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-blue-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-400 mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2 20a2.4 2.4 0 0 0 2 1.2c2.4 0 2.4-1.2 4.8-1.2 2.4 0 2.4 1.2 4.8 1.2 2.4 0 2.4-1.2 4.8-1.2 2.4 0 2.4 1.2 4.8 1.2a2.4 2.4 0 0 0 2-1.2"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase text-white mb-4">Natation</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></span>
                        Bonnet de bain (NON fourni)
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></span>
                        Lunettes de natation
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></span>
                        Combinaison (Voir règlement temp.)
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></span>
                        Trifonction (portée sous la combi)
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Bike -->
            <div class="glass-panel p-8 rounded-xl hover:border-brand-primary/50 transition-colors group">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-red-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-red-500 mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                   <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/><line x1="21.17" y1="8" x2="12" y2="8"/><line x1="3.95" y1="6.06" x2="8.54" y2="14"/><line x1="10.88" y1="21.94" x2="15.46" y2="14"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase text-white mb-4">Cyclisme</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></span>
                        Vélo (Bon état de fonctionnement)
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></span>
                        Casque (Obligatoire, norme CE)
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></span>
                        Chaussures de vélo
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></span>
                        Lunettes de soleil
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></span>
                        Bidons / Nutrition
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></span>
                        Dossard (Porté dans le dos)
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Run -->
            <div class="glass-panel p-8 rounded-xl hover:border-brand-primary/50 transition-colors group">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-green-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-green-500 mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4 15s1-1 4-1 5 2 8 2 4-1 4-1V3s-1 1-4 1-5-2-8-2-4 1-4 1z"/><line x1="4" y1="22" x2="4" y2="15"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase text-white mb-4">Course à Pied</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></span>
                        Chaussures de running
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></span>
                        Casquette / Visière
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></span>
                        Dossard (Porté devant)
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></span>
                        Chaussettes (Conseillées pour le L)
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 bg-brand-surface border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-black uppercase text-white mb-6">Sacs de Transition (M & L uniquement)</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6">
                Étant donné que le départ natation (Ensisheim) et l'arrivée (Guebwiller) sont sur des sites différents, vous devez gérer votre matériel avec soin.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-black/30 p-6 rounded-lg">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">Natation vers Vélo (T1)</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Laissez vos affaires de natation (combi, lunettes) dans le sac spécifique fourni. L'organisation transportera ce sac jusqu'à l'arrivée à Guebwiller.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-black/30 p-6 rounded-lg">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-secondary mb-2">Vélo vers Course (T2)</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Vous devez déposer votre sac d'affaires de course pied à T2 (Guebwiller) soit lors du retrait des dossards (vendredi/samedi), soit suivant les instructions spécifiques du jour de course.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    
</Layout>
